article.description: Carlik Jones had 20 points as Radford rolled past Bridgewater (VA) 91-40 on Tuesday night.
article.headline: Jones carries Radford past Bridgewater (VA) 91-40
article.story: RADFORD, Va. -- Carlik Jones had 20 points as Radford rolled past Bridgewater (VA) 91-40 on Tuesday night. Devin Hutchinson had 17 points for Radford (1-1). Travis Fields Jr. added 10 points. Devine Eke had 10 points and 10 rebounds for the home team. Chandler Murray had 17 points for the Eagles. Radford plays Georgia Southern on the road on Friday. --- For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
